name: Wallpaper lampshade, Circus Parade 14" x 300mm high
description:
A Cylinder lampshade using the fabulous Catherine Martin by Mokum, Circus Parade wallpaper, professionally hand crafted in Adelaide, South Australia using quality sourced products, quality workmanship and attention to detail. Bonded to a very durable, premium quality, white semi-transparent backing and finished with hand made bias trim top and bottom to finish. 

Available as:

14" diameter x 300mm high, suits small standard lamp base/medium table lamp base or pendant for small room

16" diameter x 300mm high, suits standard lamp base/large table lamp base or pendant for small/medium room

colour: Ruby OR Marine

Please note that the wallpaper pattern placement on the lampshade may vary from the image on this website. 

MAXIMUM WATTAGE: 15 Watt CFL

Lampshades are made to order so please allow an approximate 3-4 weeks for delivery within Australia.  Please email us to confirm expected delivery prior to ordering if preferred.

Please note you are paying for the lampshade only, it does not include a suspension kit or lamp base. Lampshades are made to fit an Australian standard size light fitting. 

Refunds: Please choose carefully as we do not accept refunds because you change your mind. We take great pride in our work, however if it is found to be faulty or damaged the return of goods must be organised within 14 days.
